- How to use
* coding
```
let starbar = DZStarBar.starBarAt(CGPoint(x: 20, y: 50), Height: 40, StarCount: 5);
starbar.addTarget(self, action: #selector(ViewController.onStarBarChanged), for: UIControlEvents.valueChanged);
starbar.currentValue = 1;
starbar.displayOnly = false;
starbar.canHalf = true;
self.view.addSubview(starbar);
```

* or use storyboard
